1. *Prestane* li da piše romane, niko neće biti tužan. (If he stops writing novels, no one will be sad.)

2. *Prestali* su da rade zajedno pre više godina. (They stopped working together many years ago.)

3. Ona je *prestala* da sluša šta muškarac govori. (She stopped listening to what the man was saying.)

4. *Prestajući* da radi, ona je počela da putuje. (By stopping working, she started travelling.)

5. *Prestanemo* li da učimo, nećemo biti uspešni. (If we stop learning, we won't be successful.)